      "span_text": "Differentiated hiPSC progeny (hFB-like cell; iFLC) were derived from hiPSC by spontaneous differentiation according to Alekseenko's method [CITATION_1] via embryoid body (EB) formation. hiPSCs 201B7 cells were suspended in polystyrene dish (SH90-15, ASAHI GLASS, Japan) containing DMEM with 10% FBS, 1% PS, and 10 µM ROCK inhibitor.",
